==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Coparcener
<hw>Co*par"ce*ner</hw> <pr>(-n⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>co-</ets> + <ets>parcener</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>One
who has an equal portion with others of an inheritance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>All the <qex>coparceners</qex> together make but one heir, and
have but one estate among them.</q> <rj><qau>Blackstone.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Coparceny</ent>⟦br⟧
